comments: Embiid (PHI) briefly places his hand on Iwundu's (ATL) back and makes marginal contact.
Maxey (PHI) brings his hand/forearm to Bogdanovic's (ATL) front during the drive and the contact is marginal.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Iwundu (ATL) and makes marginal contact to his body.

Prior to the blocked shot, Mays (ATL) establishes a legal position in Harris' (PHI) path whent he contact occurs. Mays absorbs the oncoming body contact with his forearm collapsed and his right arm remains vertical during the driving shot attempt.
Thybulle (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Iwundu (ATL) and makes marginal contact to his body.
Iwundu (ATL) makes marginal contact to Curry's (PHI) arm at the start of his drive.
Curry (PHI) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Collins (ATL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Maxey (PHI) makes contact with Bogdanovic (ATL) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Harris (PHI) places a hand/arm to Mays' (ATL) front at the start of the drive but the contact is marginal.
Maxey (PHI) receives the ball and takes more than two steps prior to the start of his dribble.
Embiid (PHI) is in a slightly wide stance but he is firming up when he absorbs the oncoming contact from Mays (ATL) to his upper body.
Embiid (PHI) lowers his shoulder and he delivers illegal contact to Collins (ATL) during the rebound.
Replay review of the shooting foul called on Collins (ATL) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Collins (ATL) dislodges Embiid (PHI) from his position during the rebound.
Iwundu (ATL) loses control of the ball and then legally regains possession of it.
